{"tid":2115970,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩爽得過WFH一早出去買個早餐睇住西裝友趕頭趕命返工","createTime":"2020-07-20T01:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T00:04:58.000Z","uid":9411,"like":14,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"08378f18000d409b96f73867c26046e406a6e251","tid":2115970,"uid":9411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:01:28.000Z","msg":"究竟要條命幾賤先要繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162f96217ae5ffd77cb10a4e6cbfff3b67f0efb4","tid":2115970,"uid":9411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d72bce7db64ab27c2b324136ae1e8854202287","tid":2115970,"uid":121255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:10:46.000Z","msg":"每個禮拜都仲要返三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08eb27f4af9b66498471eca1881f60695d9bec76","tid":2115970,"uid":71657,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:12:35.000Z","msg":"個個都唔使返工嘅話 樓豬邊得嚟買到早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef97dfd73f5b64680991c887bd1e7bb407dfe63a","tid":2115970,"uid":172190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:13:13.000Z","msg":"公墓員又贏"},{"pid":"4a8ea0218dfb59eb446e178677777a9e94c865fc","tid":2115970,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:15:50.000Z","msg":"我都想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4aaa965eab381d78f775ee834412a24de770ae","tid":2115970,"uid":37757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:17:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85a638c75e25c7a61fb559593e6f42ef2a2e0292","tid":2115970,"uid":69899,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:19:37.000Z","msg":"每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶 <br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網搵工, 每日SEND十封信差唔多, <br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂 <br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮 <br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少 <br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右, <br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活 <br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},{"pid":"91ef056ece84ebbf44e25e5730edec0acee3090a","tid":2115970,"uid":187987,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:19:54.000Z","msg":"去金鐘條天橋食著睇D公務員返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443a847d97fb73a75546e6fc16d07aabf46c6875","tid":2115970,"uid":358542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a8ea0218dfb59eb446e178677777a9e94c865fc","tid":2115970,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:15:50.000Z","msg":"我都想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:22:04.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3638db32be965ee4be64caf4fccd02d10bfd6e5","tid":2115970,"uid":323605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:22:49.000Z","msg":"公司分AB Team輪返，CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d466c7c7ff4484c30be11daa69f5c726ccd0cae","tid":2115970,"uid":121255,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b3638db32be965ee4be64caf4fccd02d10bfd6e5","tid":2115970,"uid":323605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:22:49.000Z","msg":"公司分AB Team輪返，CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets